extendedInfo.description: -- This is a Lite version of the actual App --CLICK HERE to find the full version.**** bbgeeks.com review: "Have you ever seen those personality tests that get sent around to your inbox? you know the ones that tell you if you are a great lover or what type of smurf you would be if in fact you could be a smurf..." ******** Softonic.com review: "It seems that any magazine you pick up these days will have half a dozen personality tests in it. Wouldn't it be good to do them all in one hit?" ****'Personality Psychology Pro' is a huge pack of personality tests and games presented in a pleasant / funny way. By these Psychology tests & games you can realize much more about yourself and about your companion (Sexual partner). You can analyze your personality and find out what is on your mind.You can use this program to understand yourself, to find more about a close person or to have fun with your friends. You can even impress someone by its accurate results. It is also an ideal social ice breaker. To use the application just click the option that you want to operate.FEATURES:1) Completely redesigned with high resolution graphics2) Translated into: English, German, Italian, French, Spanish, Greek.3) Over 1000 questions in personality tests.4) Personality stats for up to 3 different users.5) Birthday analysis: Chinese sign, Tree, Color, Past life.6) Graphical and textual funny tests and games.7) UpdatesDETAILS:The program consists of three major parts:1) PERSONALITY TESTS:2) FUN3) UPDATES
